    "description": "品牌管理(Brand Management；BM)乃行銷的一個重要議題。然而BM的內容基本上仍是建立在行銷管理的基本架構上，可從關係觀點（relational view）、人際關係、心理學、社會學來探討各項行銷活動，因此其範圍包括規劃、設計、執行及稽核等課題。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "ch 1 introduction 緒論<br>ch 2 customer based brand equity 以顧客為本的品牌權益<br>ch 3 品牌定位<br>ch 4 選擇品牌元素建構品牌權益<br>ch 5 設計行銷方案建構品牌權益<br>ch 6 整合行銷溝通建立品牌權益<br>ch 7 槓桿借用輔助品牌聯想建構品牌權益<br>ch 8 發展一組品牌權益衡量與管理系統<br>ch 9 衡量品牌權益來源：探取顧客的心智集合<br>ch 10 衡量品牌權益結果：探究市場績效<br>ch 11 設計與執行品牌建構策略<br>ch 12 產品命名與品牌延伸<br>ch 13 與時俱進管理品牌<br>ch 14 跨地理區與市場區隔的品牌管理<br>ch 15 結語<br><br><br>",
        "en": "ch 1 introduction <br>ch 2 customer based brand equity <br>ch 3 brand positioning<br>ch 4 build brand equity for elect brand element <br>ch 5 design marketing project for brand equity<br>ch 6 integrated marketing communication to build brand equity<br>ch 7 to leverage aided brand association to build brand equity<br>ch 8 develop a brand equity measurement and management system<br>ch 9 sources of brand equity measurement<br>ch 10 results of brand equity measurement<br>ch 11 design and execute brand build strategy<br>ch 12 product naming and brand extension<br>ch 13 management brand follow current trend<br>ch 14 management brand for cross geographical and market segmentation <br>ch 15 conclusion <br>"
    },
